<view class="vaccine-page"><view class="header"><view class="title-row"><text class="title">疫苗计划</text><view class="badge">正品保障</view></view><text class="subtitle">为您的爱宠构建免疫屏障</text></view><view class="vaccine-list"><view wx:for="{{a}}" wx:for-item="item" wx:key="f" class="vaccine-card card"><view class="card-body"><view class="v-icon"><uni-icons wx:if="{{b}}" u-i="{{item.a}}" bind:__l="__l" u-p="{{b}}"/></view><view class="v-info"><text class="v-name">{{item.b}}</text><text class="v-desc">{{item.c}}</text><view class="v-tags"><text class="tag">进口</text><text class="tag">高效</text></view></view></view><view class="card-footer"><view class="price-row"><text class="currency">¥</text><text class="price">{{item.d}}</text><text class="unit">/针</text></view><button class="book-btn" bindtap="{{item.e}}">立即预约</button></view></view></view><view class="tips-section card"><view class="tips-header"><uni-icons wx:if="{{c}}" u-i="1568d1aa-1" bind:__l="__l" u-p="{{c}}"/><text class="tips-title">接种小知识</text></view><view class="tips-content"><view class="tip-item">1. 接种前请确保宠物身体健康，无发烧、呕吐等症状。</view><view class="tip-item">2. 接种后请在医院留观20-30分钟，观察是否有过敏反应。</view><view class="tip-item">3. 接种后一周内请勿洗澡，避免剧烈运动。</view></view></view><view class="footer-spacing"></view></view>